@NODE "history" "Program History.."

   VERSIONS

 Ě v0.01 - v0.99▀ Ě These versions were all Beta development versions.
                    Only members of Micro Dimensions Software tested
                    these versions.  The program itself was very basic
                    in appearance and did not have much of a `front-end'.

 Ě v1.00 - v1.03a Ě Added support for 5 C64 bitmap formats in addition
                    to OCP Art Studio.  Coded Hires Sprite routines.

 Ě v1.04a         Ě Added Hires Sprite support and Multicolour Sprite
                    routines.

 Ě v1.05          Ě Added Hires Bitmap routine (unsurprisingly fast).

 Ě v1.06          Ě Added a progress pointer and clear bitmap code.

 Ě v1.07a         Ě FIRST RELEASE - Recoded Sprite routines, sprites now
                    use Loke's instead of the dreaded AMOS `Plot' command.
                    All calculating uses assembler commands.  Improved
                    clear bitmap routine.  Hires/Multicolour characters
                    are supported.  Added Load Address toggle.
 
@ENDNODE

